#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.corrcoef.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.corrcoef"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:1 of
msgid "Return Pearson product-moment correlation coefficients."
msgstr "返回皮尔逊积矩相关系数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:3 of
msgid ""
"Please refer to the documentation for `cov` for more detail.  The "
"relationship between the correlation coefficient matrix, `R`, and the "
"covariance matrix, `C`, is"
msgstr ""
"请参阅 `cov` 的文档以获取更多详细信息。相关系数矩阵 `R` 和协方差矩阵 `C` "
"之间的关系为"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:7 of
msgid ""
"R_{ij} = \\frac{ C_{ij} } { \\sqrt{ C_{ii} * C_{jj} } }\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:9 of
msgid "The values of `R` are between -1 and 1, inclusive."
msgstr "`R` 的值在 -1 和 1 之间（包含边界）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:11 of
msgid ""
"A 1-D or 2-D array containing multiple variables and observations. Each "
"row of `x` represents a variable, and each column a single observation of"
" all those variables. Also see `rowvar` below."
msgstr ""
"一个包含多个变量和观测值的 1-D 或 2-D 数组。`x` 的每一行代表一个变量，每"
"一列代表所有变量的一个观测值。另请参阅下面的 `rowvar`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:15 of
msgid ""
"An additional set of variables and observations. `y` has the same shape "
"as `x`."
msgstr "一组额外的变量和观测值。`y` 与 `x` 具有相同的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:18 of
msgid ""
"If `rowvar` is True (default), then each row represents a variable, with "
"observations in the columns. Otherwise, the relationship is transposed: "
"each column represents a variable, while the rows contain observations."
msgstr ""
"如果 `rowvar` 为 True（默认值），则每行代表一个变量，列为观测值。否则，"
"关系将转置：每列表示一个变量，而行包含观测值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:24 of
msgid "**R** -- The correlation coefficient matrix of the variables."
msgstr "**R** —— 变量的相关系数矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`cov`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:30 of
msgid "Covariance matrix"
msgstr "协方差矩阵"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:33 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:34 of
msgid ""
"Due to floating point rounding the resulting tensor may not be Hermitian,"
" the diagonal elements may not be 1, and the elements may not satisfy the"
" inequality abs(a) <= 1. The real and imaginary parts are clipped to the "
"interval [-1,  1] in an attempt to improve on that situation but is not "
"much help in the complex case."
msgstr ""
"由于浮点数舍入，结果张量可能不是厄米特矩阵，对角线元素可能不为 1，元素"
"可能不满足不等式 abs(a) <= 1。实部和虚部被裁剪到区间 [-1, 1] 以尝试改善"
"这种情况，但在复数情况下帮助不大。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.corrcoef.corrcoef:40 of
msgid ""
"This function accepts but discards arguments `bias` and `ddof`.  This is "
"for backwards compatibility with previous versions of this function.  "
"These arguments had no effect on the return values of the function and "
"can be safely ignored in this and previous versions of numpy."
msgstr ""
"此函数接受但忽略参数 `bias` 和 `ddof`。这是为了与该函数的早期版本向后兼容"
"。这些参数对函数的返回值没有影响，在此版本及以前版本的 numpy 中可以安全"
"忽略。"

